## Common Moodle DOM Patterns

| Element | Selector |
|---|---|
| Session key | `M.cfg.sesskey` (JS global) |
| Context ID | `document.body.className.match(/context-(\d+)/)` |
| Course ID | URL param `id` on course pages |
| User menu | `.usermenu .usertext` |
| Activity links | `a[href*="/mod/"]` |
| File manager widget | `.filemanager` |
| Draft item ID | `input[name=files_filemanager]` |
| Submit button | `#id_submitbutton` |
| Status table | `.generaltable td, .generaltable th` |
| Alerts/notices | `.alert, .notifysuccess, .notifyproblem` |

## Error Patterns

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| "Invalid context id" | Wrong `ctx_id` | Extract from `body.className` |
| "Call to undefined method repository_*::upload()" | Wrong `repo_id` — that repo type doesn't support uploads | Try other repo_ids (see Step 3) |
| "Không được phép truy cập kho này" | Permission denied on that repo | Skip, try next repo_id |
| "ID kho không hợp lệ" | repo_id doesn't exist | Stop, you've gone past valid range |
| Login redirect | Session expired | User must re-authenticate via OAuth |
